<paragraph id="IAS41_13" base="SL33606" principles="yes"><paranum>13</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 41"/><data name="paranum" value="13"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS41_P0163"><xref base="SL143219" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0107">Agricultural produce<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0011"/></ph></xref> harvested from an entity&#x2019;s <xref base="SL143220" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0108">biological assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0021"/></ph></xref> shall be measured at its <xref base="SL143246" href="IAS41_8.dita#IAS41_8/IAS41_P0150">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> less <xref base="F6127376" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0110">costs to sell<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0059"/></ph></xref>  at the point of <xref base="SL143223" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0114">harvest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0163"/></ph></xref>. Such measurement is the cost at that date when applying <xref id="IAS41_X0124" base="F391380" href="../IAS02.ditamap">IAS 2 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Inventories</ph></ph></xref> or another applicable Standard.</p></body></paragraph>